                  </persName>
            . I was going to Mr. Frazier's house, and<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="182207030019"></xptr>met the prisoner coming out of the gate - he went towards town; the great coat was under his left arm. He was pursued.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I was in distress.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 42.</p>
               <p>Of <rs id="t18220703-35-verdict189" type="verdictDescription">
